<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">最重要的是历历  你的帮助是必须的</font>

135
00:06:25,580 --> 00:06:27,870
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">既然你这么说  我知道了</font>

136
00:06:28,700 --> 00:06:31,110
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那么  第三个请求是什么</font>

137
00:06:31,110 --> 00:06:31,310
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（不得不答应）</font>

138
00:06:31,550 --> 00:06:34,440
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">第三个请求你刚才已经替我说了</font>

139
00:06:34,840 --> 00:06:39,940
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">第三个请求就是让你去请骏河来帮忙</font>

140
00:06:40,590 --> 00:06:42,830
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">既然所有的请求你都接受了的话</font>

141
00:06:43,310 --> 00:06:45,450
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">{\an8}我这边也能帮助历历了</font>

142
00:06:45,450 --> 00:06:46,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我这边也能帮助历历了</font>

143
00:06:45,450 --> 00:06:46,200
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}(接受)</font>

144
00:06:46,620 --> 00:06:51,170
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">卧烟姐姐放心了  很高兴能助你一臂之力</font>

145
00:06:51,910 --> 00:06:52,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是嘛</font>

146
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:53,130
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（完全不能放心）</font>

147
00:06:53,130 --> 00:06:53,420
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（小忍的状况）</font>

148
00:06:53,420 --> 00:06:53,800
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（无法忍耐）</font>

149
00:06:55,070 --> 00:06:56,960
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那个  不好意思  卧烟小姐</font>

150
00:06:57,320 --> 00:07:00,500
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">既然已经答应了  能不能一边赶路一边说呢</font>

151
00:07:01,080 --> 00:07:02,720
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我想尽早和小忍见面</font>

152
00:07:03,020 --> 00:07:08,310
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">历历  听我一句话  你们现在不可以从这里离开</font>

153
00:07:08,310 --> 00:07:08,520
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（严）</font>

154
00:07:08,520 --> 00:07:08,730
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（严厉）</font>

155
00:07:08,730 --> 00:07:09,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（严厉的声音）</font>

156
00:07:09,200 --> 00:07:13,260
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">至少也要等到我把话说完</font>

157
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:18,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">回到小镇是最坏的选择</font>

158
00:07:18,610 --> 00:07:18,780
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（不说清楚的话）</font>

159
00:07:18,780 --> 00:07:18,990
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（你也不明白）</font>

160
00:07:18,990 --> 00:07:19,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（我先说在前面）</font>

161
00:07:20,060 --> 00:07:21,920
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">只有那件事千万不能做</font>

162
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:27,100
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">现在你们还是待在这里吧</font>

163
00:07:27,420 --> 00:07:30,330
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">逃到这种偏僻的地方才是正确的选择</font>

164
00:07:31,140 --> 00:07:35,210
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是  正因此我才会和小忍分隔两地</font>

165
00:07:35,390 --> 00:07:40,300
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你们的联系不久便会恢复  关于那一点我向你保证</font>

166
00:07:40,470 --> 00:07:44,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">可是  让小忍单独行动的话不是很危险吗</font>

167
00:07:44,620 --> 00:07:46,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">被盯上的可是她呀</font>

168
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:53,150
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">嗯  看来我应该早点把「被盯上的是小忍」这个误解给解开啊</font>

169
00:07:53,400 --> 00:07:53,860
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">哎？</font>

170
00:07:53,900 --> 00:07:54,150
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（不假思索）</font>

171
00:07:54,150 --> 00:07:54,480
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（反问道）</font>

172
00:07:54,710 --> 00:07:58,540
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">被盯上的不是小忍吗？</font>

173
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:03,440
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">四百年前的确是这样  但这次不是</font>

174
00:08:04,820 --> 00:08:10,160
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那么  这次现象的目标是谁  你自然也是知道的吧</font>

175
00:08:10,300 --> 00:08:11,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">当然</font>

176
00:08:11,250 --> 00:08:11,410
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（经验法则）</font>

177
00:08:11,410 --> 00:08:11,710
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（那至多只是）</font>

178
00:08:11,710 --> 00:08:12,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（可能性罢了）</font>

179
00:08:12,180 --> 00:08:16,790
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这次被「黑暗」盯上的是  那个累坏了睡在那边的孩子</font>

180
00:08:17,540 --> 00:08:17,920
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">哎？</font>

181
00:08:18,140 --> 00:08:18,880
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也就是</font>

182
00:08:22,030 --> 00:08:23,430
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">八九寺真宵妹妹</font>

183
00:08:24,930 --> 00:08:25,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（我看着八九寺）</font>

184
00:08:25,140 --> 00:08:25,390
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（累坏了睡得正香的八九寺）</font>

185
00:08:25,390 --> 00:08:25,720
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（和我感情最深的幽灵少女）</font>

186
00:08:28,140 --> 00:08:29,060
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是…八九寺？</font>

187
00:08:29,310 --> 00:08:30,100
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">原来如此</font>

188
00:08:30,390 --> 00:08:32,770
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我之前也想过可能是这样</font>

189
00:08:33,070 --> 00:08:35,150
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是这样吗  斧乃木妹妹</font>

190
00:08:35,460 --> 00:08:38,230
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我从姐姐那边也听说过一些</font>

191
00:08:38,510 --> 00:08:41,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不过哪边都有可能</font>

192
00:08:41,350 --> 00:08:44,490
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不  说起来  也有可能是鬼哥哥</font>

193
00:08:45,390 --> 00:08:50,080
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是我想最有可能的还是八九寺小姐</font>

194
00:08:50,620 --> 00:08:51,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这到底是怎么回事</font>

195
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:52,160
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（朝着八九寺）</font>

196
00:08:52,160 --> 00:08:52,330
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（——似的）</font>

197
00:08:52,330 --> 00:08:52,620
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（盯着八九寺）</font>

198
00:08:52,620 --> 00:08:52,870
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（——似的）</font>

199
00:08:52,870 --> 00:08:53,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（我也感觉到）</font>

200
00:08:53,310 --> 00:08:55,420
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这个问题还是我来回答吧</font>

201
00:08:55,790 --> 00:08:58,040
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因为我正是为了这个才来这里的</font>

202
00:08:59,420 --> 00:09:04,600
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">「黑暗」不是怪异  它是怪异之外的存在  非存在</font>

203
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:05,010
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（并不存在的非存在）</font>

204
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:06,590
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">无法打倒它</font>

205
00:09:06,590 --> 00:09:06,760
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（打倒）</font>

206
00:09:07,030 --> 00:09:08,350
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">无法杀死它</font>

207
00:09:08,350 --> 00:09:08,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（杀死）</font>

208
00:09:08,740 --> 00:09:10,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">当然  也无法吞了它</font>

209
00:09:10,220 --> 00:09:10,430
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（吞食）</font>

210
00:09:10,870 --> 00:09:12,430
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就是这么不讲理  就是这么不合理</font>

211
00:09:12,660 --> 00:09:14,080
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这就是那个非存在</font>

212
00:09:14,460 --> 00:09:15,990
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">并不存在的某个东西</font>

213
00:09:16,460 --> 00:09:18,990
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">能将怪异的存在消灭的某个东西</font>

214
00:09:20,110 --> 00:09:20,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（和物质相对的反物质）</font>

215
00:09:20,280 --> 00:09:20,610
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（和怪异相对的反怪异）</font>

216
00:09:20,610 --> 00:09:20,820
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（冲撞之后便会消灭）</font>

217
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:27,370
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说到被盯上的理由  倒也不是不讲理  也不是不合理</font>

218
00:09:27,630 --> 00:09:32,390
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">严格来说  它盯上的是偏离怪异之道的怪异</font>

219
00:09:33,100 --> 00:09:36,990
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">偏离人道的人会被社会排除的吧</font>

220
00:09:37,380 --> 00:09:42,630
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">同样  偏离怪异之道的怪异  便会被世界所排除</font>

221
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:44,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">通过一种超越常理的力量</font>

222
00:09:45,130 --> 00:09:45,630
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（历/质疑）</font>

223
00:09:46,500 --> 00:09:47,750
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">还不明白吗</font>

224
00:09:48,350 --> 00:09:52,790
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那就具体一点  想想小忍在四百年前都做了些什么</font>

225
00:09:53,710 --> 00:09:55,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是的  没错  就是这样</font>

226
00:09:56,430 --> 00:09:59,480
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">小忍在四百年前  扮演了神的角色</font>

227
00:09:59,480 --> 00:09:59,810
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（明明是个鬼  却扮演了神）</font>

228
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:07,530
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你是想说小忍并没有自称为神  只是周围的人把她误解成了神对吧</font>

229
00:10:07,760 --> 00:10:08,410
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是</font>

230
00:10:08,790 --> 00:10:13,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不努力试图解开误解  和说谎是一样的</font>

231
00:10:13,990 --> 00:10:18,710
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">变成神这件事并没有什么好指责的</font>

232
00:10:19,020 --> 00:10:20,550
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是说谎是不好的</font>

233
00:10:20,990 --> 00:10:25,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不是变成神不好  而是骗别人认为自己是神不好</font>

234
00:10:25,540 --> 00:10:28,130
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这就是她成为制裁对象的原因</font>

235
00:10:28,940 --> 00:10:32,600
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这样一来小忍能从非存在那边逃离的原因也清楚了吧</font>

236
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:32,810
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（明确了）</font>

237
00:10:33,180 --> 00:10:38,670
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">她大跳跃逃到南极的同时  也做出了吸血鬼该有的行为</font>

238
00:10:39,140 --> 00:10:40,360
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">制造眷属</font>

239
00:10:40,710 --> 00:10:42,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这就暴露了她假装是神的谎言</font>

240
00:10:43,310 --> 00:10:46,740
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">于是非存在便失去了行动的理由</font>

241
00:10:47,230 --> 00:10:49,950
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">到头来小忍还是受到了制裁</font>

242
00:10:49,950 --> 00:10:50,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（目击者被消灭）</font>

243
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:50,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（证人不再存在）</font>

244
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:50,530
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（犯人的谎言暴露）</font>

245
00:10:50,530 --> 00:10:50,870
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（怪异再也无法伪装自己）</font>

246
00:10:51,100 --> 00:10:56,070
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">现在它也没有理由会盯上小忍  所以她是安全的</font>

247
00:10:56,470 --> 00:10:58,710
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那么不安全的又是谁呢</font>

248
00:10:58,920 --> 00:10:59,710
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你自然也知道了吧</font>

249
00:11:00,390 --> 00:11:04,590
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">八九寺真宵  就是你咯  小骗子</font>

250
00:11:04,980 --> 00:11:07,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">首先不要再给我装睡了！</font>

251
00:11:09,710 --> 00:11:10,820
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">阿良良木先生</font>

252
00:11:11,300 --> 00:11:13,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没事的  冷静下来</font>

253
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:17,160
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">虽然现在还不清楚情况  总之我是站在你这边的</font>

254
00:11:17,700 --> 00:11:18,270
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">嗯</font>

255
00:11:18,550 --> 00:11:19,940
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这到底是怎么回事</font>

256
00:11:20,420 --> 00:11:24,150
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这孩子她  八九寺她  到底说了什么谎</font>

257
00:11:24,150 --> 00:11:24,440
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（到现在还全都是些不明白的事情）</font>

258
00:11:24,740 --> 00:11:29,320
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">真宵所撒的谎  就是「至今还存在于此」这个谎言</font>

259
00:11:29,450 --> 00:11:29,700
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（想看到小忍）</font>

260
00:11:29,700 --> 00:11:29,950
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（想看到战场原和羽川）</font>

261
00:11:29,950 --> 00:11:30,160
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（想看到火怜和月火）</font>

262
00:11:31,910 --> 00:11:36,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">其实应该已经成佛了吧  小真宵</font>

263
00:11:36,290 --> 00:11:36,450
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（至少）</font>

264
00:11:36,450 --> 00:11:36,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（不想看到这些——）</font>

265
00:11:36,660 --> 00:11:37,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（真相）</font>

266
00:11:37,350 --> 00:11:42,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是你依旧存在于此  继续着这样的谎言</font>

267
00:11:42,380 --> 00:11:44,270
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">「存在于此」的谎言</font>

268
00:11:44,700 --> 00:11:48,830
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这自然会惹人生气了  就算不是非存在也要生气了呢</font>

269
00:11:49,240 --> 00:11:53,340
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我并没想过…要说谎</font>

270
00:11:53,590 --> 00:11:57,500
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我已经说过  放任误解就是说谎  八九寺真宵妹妹</font>

271
00:11:57,880 --> 00:12:01,640
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">简单来说你现在就像是幽灵死后的幽灵一般的存在</font>

272
00:12:02,060 --> 00:12:06,470
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">遗憾的是世间并不承认这种复杂构造的存在</font>

273
00:12:06,990 --> 00:12:10,420
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这样的存在注定会被非存在给吞噬</font>

274
00:12:10,740 --> 00:12:12,860
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">幽灵死后的幽灵…</font>

275
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:17,260
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">八九寺真宵是十一年前死于交通事故的幽灵</font>

276
00:12:17,780 --> 00:12:21,710
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">严格地说应该是被称为迷途之牛的蜗牛怪异</font>

277
00:12:21,710 --> 00:12:22,080
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（迷途之牛）</font>

278
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:22,620
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（让人迷失方向的怪异）</font>

279
00:12:22,820 --> 00:12:28,870
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是这件事却被历历和历历的女朋友  还有不成熟的咩咩解决了</font>

280
00:12:29,310 --> 00:12:31,630
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">真宵的迷途已经消失了</font>

281
00:12:31,940 --> 00:12:34,500
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是这孩子却依旧存在于此</font>

282
00:12:34,900 --> 00:12:36,470
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这不是谎言是什么</font>

283
00:12:37,510 --> 00:12:37,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（至少）</font>

284
00:12:37,680 --> 00:12:37,970
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（八九寺真宵）</font>

285
00:12:37,970 --> 00:12:38,260
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（不是迷途之牛）</font>

286
00:12:38,590 --> 00:12:42,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">只要她还是迷途之牛  就不得不让人迷路</font>

287
00:12:42,540 --> 00:12:44,150
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是她却没这么做</font>

288
00:12:44,150 --> 00:12:44,350
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（身为怪异的角色设定）</font>

289
00:12:44,350 --> 00:12:44,690
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（就是这么严格）</font>

290
00:12:44,980 --> 00:12:48,110
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我曾和八九寺一起去过战场原的家</font>

291
00:12:48,760 --> 00:12:51,500
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">却没和八九寺一起迷过路</font>

292
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:55,760
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">倒不如说她常常为我指明前进的方向</font>

293
00:12:57,270 --> 00:13:01,230
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">所以我以为八九寺不再是迷途之牛了</font>

294
00:13:01,900 --> 00:13:04,080
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我便是这样看待八九寺的</font>

295
00:13:04,900 --> 00:13:07,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我便是这样目击的</font>

296
00:13:08,170 --> 00:13:08,880
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（我便是这样——被骗的）</font>

297
00:13:09,110 --> 00:13:11,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">真是精彩的障眼法呢</font>

298
00:13:11,390 --> 00:13:13,630
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但那已经是为时已晚了吧</font>

299
00:13:14,110 --> 00:13:17,860
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这孩子真的没从一开始就对历历说谎吗</font>

300
00:13:18,060 --> 00:13:20,100
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没有  八九寺她…</font>

301
00:13:20,830 --> 00:13:24,350
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">八九寺没有对我说过谎</font>

302
00:13:24,910 --> 00:13:26,950
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">从一开始就是  一次都没有</font>

303
00:13:27,230 --> 00:13:28,320
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">阿良良木先生…</font>

304
00:13:28,860 --> 00:13:29,070
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（但是我现在却无法直视她）</font>

305
00:13:29,070 --> 00:13:29,360
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（我）</font>

306
00:13:29,360 --> 00:13:29,730
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（只好面对着卧烟小姐）</font>

307
00:13:29,940 --> 00:13:34,100
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是啊  没错  刚才那是我的误会</font>

308
00:13:34,440 --> 00:13:37,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">她其实是在对自己撒谎吧</font>

309
00:13:38,620 --> 00:13:40,030
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">嗯  不管怎么说</font>

310
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:43,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">既然她已经偏离了迷途之牛的道路</font>

311
00:13:43,380 --> 00:13:46,040
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">小真宵就要被惩罚  被制裁了</font>

312
00:13:46,310 --> 00:13:48,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">被惩罚  被制裁…</font>

313
00:13:49,180 --> 00:13:50,400
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">怎么会…但是…</font>

314
00:13:51,350 --> 00:13:53,940
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是  现在我们不是还没有证据吗</font>

315
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:57,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">还不能肯定被盯上的就是八九寺</font>

316
00:13:57,660 --> 00:14:02,710
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">的确是没有实证  但有几个状况已经可以证明了</font>

317
00:14:03,220 --> 00:14:07,160
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">黑暗在小真宵失去意识的时候并没有追过来吧</font>

318
00:14:08,990 --> 00:14:12,110
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那么…在那之后…逃到山里之后也是</font>

319
00:14:12,350 --> 00:14:14,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是因为她大部分时间都累倒睡着</font>

320
00:14:14,980 --> 00:14:16,750
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">所以那东西才没有追过来？</font>

321
00:14:19,120 --> 00:14:19,320
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（会消耗体力）</font>

322
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:19,570
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（的山里）</font>

323
00:14:19,570 --> 00:14:19,780
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（一起赶路——）</font>

324
00:14:20,620 --> 00:14:20,830
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（不知道该往哪里走）</font>

325
00:14:20,830 --> 00:14:21,080
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（在下山路上）</font>

326
00:14:21,080 --> 00:14:21,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（在逃跑路上——）</font>

327
00:14:22,410 --> 00:14:23,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（迷路了好一段时间——）</font>

328
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:28,420
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没错  现在你正在迷路</font>

329
00:14:29,040 --> 00:14:33,860
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">在这个状况下  可以视作小真宵在履行身为迷途之牛的本分吧</font>

330
00:14:34,630 --> 00:14:36,920
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">所以  黑暗才不会出现</font>

331
00:14:36,920 --> 00:14:37,130
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（不会在小忍那里出现）</font>

332
00:14:37,130 --> 00:14:37,430
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（也不会在八九寺这里出现）</font>

333
00:14:37,590 --> 00:14:43,630
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">相反  如果历历你们回到自己的镇上  回到自己家里的话</font>

334
00:14:44,160 --> 00:14:47,770
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">又会变成小真宵失去了作为怪异本分的状况</font>

335
00:14:48,900 --> 00:14:49,100
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（没有什么不对）</font>

336
00:14:49,100 --> 00:14:49,400
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（没有谁不对）</font>

337
00:14:49,400 --> 00:14:49,770
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（必定会出现——这样的局面）</font>

338
00:14:49,940 --> 00:14:53,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那么…那么  我们该怎么办才好</font>

339
00:14:53,460 --> 00:14:55,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">难道要让八九寺再变回迷途之牛吗</font>

340
00:14:56,190 --> 00:14:58,440
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">只要像以前那样  继续让人迷路…</font>

341
00:14:58,440 --> 00:14:59,450
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我不愿意！</font>

342
00:14:59,450 --> 00:14:59,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（结论只有这一个）</font>

343
00:14:59,660 --> 00:14:59,910
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（停止说谎）</font>

344
00:14:59,910 --> 00:15:00,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（说实话就好了——）</font>

345
00:15:00,430 --> 00:15:02,910
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那种事  我已经不想再做第二次了</font>

346
00:15:04,060 --> 00:15:06,430
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">八九寺  但是…</font>

347
00:15:06,680 --> 00:15:11,070
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">托阿良良木先生的福  我才不用继续做那种事</font>

348
00:15:11,600 --> 00:15:13,880
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我才能回到了自己的家</font>

349
00:15:14,240 --> 00:15:17,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">所以  我再也不想做那种事了</font>

350
00:15:17,710 --> 00:15:19,780
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">「再也不去做那种事」</font>

351
00:15:20,350 --> 00:15:22,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我早就决定要说这样一个谎言</font>

352
00:15:23,810 --> 00:15:24,100
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（正常地生活下去就好了）</font>

353
00:15:24,100 --> 00:15:24,470
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（作为怪异——）</font>

354
00:15:24,590 --> 00:15:28,870
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">卧…卧烟小姐  那有没有能打倒那个黑暗的办法</font>

355
00:15:29,030 --> 00:15:31,800
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我都说过那根本不是可以打倒的东西</font>

356
00:15:31,950 --> 00:15:34,430
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那是一种法则一样的东西</font>

357
00:15:35,270 --> 00:15:35,610
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（无法反驳）</font>

358
00:15:35,610 --> 00:15:35,820
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（这种事情——）</font>

359
00:15:35,820 --> 00:15:36,150
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（从没有过）</font>

360
00:15:37,640 --> 00:15:40,030
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没事的  阿良良木先生</font>

361
00:15:40,350 --> 00:15:42,590
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这样的话  还是有办法的</font>

362
00:15:43,430 --> 00:15:44,500
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">办法是…？</font>

363
00:15:44,830 --> 00:15:50,360
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就像平时那样就好了  说到底还是要按照规则去处理</font>

364
00:15:50,790 --> 00:15:54,420
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">按规则…什么意思啊  八九寺</font>

365
00:15:54,420 --> 00:15:54,670
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（敌人就是法则本身）</font>

366
00:15:54,900 --> 00:15:55,870
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">具体来说…</font>

367
00:15:55,750 --> 00:15:56,050
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（破坏法则）</font>

368
00:15:56,050 --> 00:15:56,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（是不可能的）</font>

369
00:15:56,560 --> 00:15:57,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">具体来说…</font>

370
00:15:58,820 --> 00:16:00,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">只要我消失就可以了</font>

371
00:16:02,900 --> 00:16:05,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">卧烟小姐很干脆地回去了</font>

372
00:16:06,150 --> 00:16:10,620
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">留给了我手机号码  说是等我的联络</font>

373
00:16:11,900 --> 00:16:15,820
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">斧乃木妹妹  为什么你没跟着一起走</font>

374
00:16:15,960 --> 00:16:19,390
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没什么  因为我也是和你们一起迷路的</font>

375
00:16:19,880 --> 00:16:24,710
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">如果我现在回去了  黑暗也许还会发动</font>

376
00:16:25,120 --> 00:16:27,720
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是吗  你人真好</font>

377
00:16:28,590 --> 00:16:30,720
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是啊  阿良良木先生</font>

378
00:16:31,300 --> 00:16:34,320
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这些  不是我一个人的问题</font>

379
00:16:36,080 --> 00:16:42,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">阿良良木先生  你想让我体会四百年前忍小姐的心情吗</font>

380
00:16:44,740 --> 00:16:46,940
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">如果不是  就请放开手吧</font>

381
00:16:48,040 --> 00:16:50,070
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这种说法  太卑鄙了</font>

382
00:16:52,080 --> 00:16:57,160
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">其实五月母亲节的那个时候  你就已经让我成佛了</font>

383
00:16:58,140 --> 00:17:00,790
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">现在就像是加时赛一样</font>

384
00:17:01,310 --> 00:17:03,530
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不…不是加时赛</font>

385
00:17:03,780 --> 00:17:05,190
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">应该是奖励关才对</font>

386
00:17:05,820 --> 00:17:10,720
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我也没觉得会这样永远持续下去  总有一天会结束的</font>

387
00:17:11,190 --> 00:17:15,940
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">虽然比想象的要来得突然  但是呢  世事就是这样嘛</font>

388
00:17:20,040 --> 00:17:22,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我还跑到阿良良木先生的家里睡觉</font>

389
00:17:22,350 --> 00:17:25,460
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就算是撒谎这也未免太过自由了吧</font>

390
00:17:25,910 --> 00:17:28,500
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">只是因为和阿良良木先生聊天很开心</font>

391
00:17:28,960 --> 00:17:32,460
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就一次次把去那个世界的日期延后</font>

392
00:17:33,380 --> 00:17:37,440
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">虽然总是想这样开心的日子要一直持续下去就好了</font>

393
00:17:37,790 --> 00:17:41,560
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不…等一下  不要做总结性发言好不好</font>

394
00:17:42,200 --> 00:17:45,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我马上就再想想  一定会有什么办法</font>

395
00:17:45,380 --> 00:17:46,780
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">现在开始才是颠覆剧本…</font>

396
00:17:46,780 --> 00:17:47,710
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不会有的！</font>

397
00:17:48,040 --> 00:17:49,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不会有突破口的…</font>

398
00:17:50,310 --> 00:17:53,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不如说  这个世界还是挺仁慈的不是吗</font>

399
00:17:53,900 --> 00:17:56,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">一般来说是不会等我这几个月的</font>

400
00:17:56,470 --> 00:18:00,030
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">幽灵的幽灵  这样的存在太过荒诞无稽了</font>

401
00:18:00,400 --> 00:18:01,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">怎么会…</font>

402
00:18:01,880 --> 00:18:07,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是这种要八九寺背负一切责任  好让其他人得救的做法也…</font>

403
00:18:08,550 --> 00:18:14,600
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说什么呢阿良良木先生  你不就是这么过来的吗</font>

404
00:18:15,030 --> 00:18:19,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">只让自己做不让别人做  这可怎么说得过去呢</font>

405
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:23,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">为什么…为什么你就能这么淡定啊</font>

406
00:18:24,200 --> 00:18:27,820
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">的确  我看起来确实是这样过来的</font>

407
00:18:28,160 --> 00:18:30,830
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但我从来没有坦然自若地去做过这种事</font>

408
00:18:31,700 --> 00:18:36,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">一直都是一边强忍着眼泪  或者应该说一边流着眼泪一边战斗</font>

409
00:18:37,430 --> 00:18:42,210
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">可你却为什么能这样  没有一点不安  没有一点不满…</font>

410
00:18:42,590 --> 00:18:45,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说我没有一点不安的确是骗人</font>

411
00:18:45,660 --> 00:18:47,720
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但不满可真是一点都没有</font>

412
00:18:48,120 --> 00:18:49,320
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我过得很开心</font>

413
00:18:49,860 --> 00:18:53,060
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而且今后还能在天上守着阿良良木先生</font>

414
00:18:53,200 --> 00:18:55,060
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">都说了别再说这种话了好不好</font>

415
00:18:57,430 --> 00:19:00,860
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">啊  「消失」这个词听上去不太好</font>

416
00:19:01,280 --> 00:19:03,990
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我是要「回家」了  阿良良木先生</font>

417
00:19:04,670 --> 00:19:08,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">虽然人会不在了  但存在过的事实不会消失</font>

418
00:19:09,100 --> 00:19:13,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这又有什么区别  只是字面上不同…</font>

419
00:19:13,540 --> 00:19:15,920
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">该放弃时就放弃吧  鬼哥哥</font>

420
00:19:16,480 --> 00:19:21,550
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">都搞不清谁是小孩子了  人家自己不都说没关系了吗</font>

421
00:19:21,990 --> 00:19:23,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是啊  阿良良木先生</font>

422
00:19:24,300 --> 00:19:26,340
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我都说没关系了</font>

423
00:19:26,390 --> 00:19:32,300
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">真是个不懂事的孩子！别老想着自己  你也替我想想好吗</font>

424
00:19:32,620 --> 00:19:36,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">如果知道事情变成这样  我宁可和你迷路一辈子</font>

425
00:19:37,820 --> 00:19:38,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">阿良良木先生…</font>

426
00:19:39,460 --> 00:19:41,690
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">啊对了  还有这个办法啊</font>

427
00:19:42,100 --> 00:19:43,910
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这样不就解决一切了吗</font>

428
00:19:44,200 --> 00:19:46,070
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不管是山里还是偏僻的村子</font>

429
00:19:46,270 --> 00:19:48,550
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">只要和你一辈子迷路下去就好了</font>

430
00:19:48,920 --> 00:19:53,070
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这样一来  你就能继续履行迷路蜗牛的本分了</font>

431
00:19:53,380 --> 00:19:54,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">一点问题都没有</font>

432
00:19:54,670 --> 00:19:55,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">阿良良木先生…</font>

433
00:19:55,510 --> 00:19:58,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">对  我决定了  就这么做</font>

434
00:19:58,540 --> 00:20:03,310
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">虽然我这个半吊子吸血鬼还能活多久也不知道</font>

435
00:20:03,740 --> 00:20:06,340
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但活个十年二十年还是…</font>

436
00:20:06,340 --> 00:20:07,420
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">阿良良木先生！</font>

437
00:20:08,790 --> 00:20:15,710
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你说什么呢  为了我要花上二十年…战场原小姐怎么办</font>

438
00:20:16,160 --> 00:20:19,830
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">羽川小姐呢…还有你的妹妹们怎么办</font>

439
00:20:20,280 --> 00:20:24,820
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就算能带上忍小姐  但她们该怎么办</font>

440
00:20:25,020 --> 00:20:28,780
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这个…嗯  一个一个再想就好了</font>

441
00:20:29,110 --> 00:20:30,720
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">再怎么想也不行吧</font>

442
00:20:30,990 --> 00:20:35,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没办法一次都选的  没错  不会像意大利的绅士那样…</font>

443
00:20:36,430 --> 00:20:39,060
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">意大利的绅士也做不到吧</font>

444
00:20:41,220 --> 00:20:43,070
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这不是挺好的嘛  阿良良木先生</font>

445
00:20:43,700 --> 00:20:45,790
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">「即便分开两个人的心还是在一起」</font>

446
00:20:46,100 --> 00:20:48,320
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">「心中的回忆永远不会消失」</font>

447
00:20:48,710 --> 00:20:50,740
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">「我永远都在你的身边」</font>

448
00:20:51,110 --> 00:20:53,230
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">「两个人的羁绊会直到永远」</font>

449
00:20:53,600 --> 00:20:58,760
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">「虽然离开  但有一天你有麻烦时我肯定还会回来」</font>

450
00:20:59,150 --> 00:21:01,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">请用这样的理由说服自己好吗</font>

451
00:21:02,540 --> 00:21:04,850
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我怎么可能被那种烂理由说服！</font>

452
00:21:05,040 --> 00:21:05,860
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">开什么玩笑！</font>

453
00:21:09,110 --> 00:21:11,490
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就这样吧  阿良良木先生</font>

454
00:21:14,990 --> 00:21:18,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">能和阿良良木先生愉快聊天的这三个月</font>

455
00:21:18,740 --> 00:21:24,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">已经足以弥补我独自一人迷路的十一年了</font>

456
00:21:25,520 --> 00:21:29,150
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">所以就这样吧  谢谢你</font>

457
00:21:30,720 --> 00:21:34,720
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">啊对了  阿良良木先生  最后再来一次那个吧</font>

458
00:21:34,980 --> 00:21:35,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那个是…</font>

459
00:21:36,020 --> 00:21:38,430
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">从「舌头打结了」开始的一系列</font>

460
00:21:38,740 --> 00:21:42,040
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">什么嘛  你果然还是故意的啊</font>

461
00:21:42,200 --> 00:21:46,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那当然了  有谁的舌头会打结成那样啊</font>

462
00:21:46,720 --> 00:21:48,230
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">{\an8}好吗  阿良良木先生</font>

463
00:21:48,520 --> 00:21:51,190
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">{\an8}说起来这次还一次都没说过呢</font>

464
00:21:52,630 --> 00:21:56,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">阿良良木先生  就当是为我饯行  请你一定要说一次</font>

465
00:21:58,800 --> 00:21:59,710
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我知道了</font>

466
00:22:19,980 --> 00:22:22,360
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不好意思  舌头打结了</font>

467
00:22:25,500 --> 00:22:28,390
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">最喜欢你了  阿良良木先生</font>

468
00:22:29,680 --> 00:22:36,790
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}今もずっとその声を覚えてるから</font>

469
00:22:29,680 --> 00:22:36,790
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">现在我也记得你的声音</font>

470
00:22:46,280 --> 00:22:48,890
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}あの日走った道に</font>

471
00:22:46,280 --> 00:22:48,890
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">那些日子走过的路</font>

472
00:22:49,090 --> 00:22:51,710
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}あの日見上げた空に</font>

473
00:22:49,090 --> 00:22:51,710
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">那些日子仰望的天空</font>

474
00:22:51,950 --> 00:22:56,960
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}二度と返らない時を重ねてる</font>

475
00:22:51,950 --> 00:22:56,960
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">无法回去的曾经反复叠加</font>

476
00:22:57,520 --> 00:23:00,160
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}君は笑うだろうか</font>

477
00:22:57,520 --> 00:23:00,160
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">你恐怕会笑我吧</font>

478
00:23:00,290 --> 00:23:02,950
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}少し怒るだろうね</font>

479
00:23:00,290 --> 00:23:02,950
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">会有一丝生气吧</font>

480
00:23:03,170 --> 00:23:08,680
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}こんな諦め悪い僕のことを</font>

481
00:23:03,170 --> 00:23:08,680
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">我就是这么一个无法死心的人</font>

482
00:23:09,330 --> 00:23:12,370
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}何度でも</font>

483
00:23:09,330 --> 00:23:12,370
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">一次又一次</font>

484
00:23:12,680 --> 00:23:18,310
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}迂闊に願う可能性を清書して  （いつまでも）</font>

485
00:23:12,680 --> 00:23:18,310
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">将那些恍惚间许愿的可能性整理起来  （直到永远）</font>

486
00:23:18,310 --> 00:23:22,880
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}まだ迷いそうに騙されてたくて</font>

487
00:23:18,310 --> 00:23:22,880
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">都想这样迷茫地被自己所欺骗</font>

488
00:23:23,320 --> 00:23:28,440
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}だから「どうかせめて」なんて思う心は</font>

489
00:23:23,320 --> 00:23:28,440
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">因此许下这些愿望的心情</font>

490
00:23:28,570 --> 00:23:31,930
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}一時的な感傷だって</font>

491
00:23:28,570 --> 00:23:31,930
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">这些暂时的感伤</font>

492
00:23:32,130 --> 00:23:34,400
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}許せばいい</font>

493
00:23:32,130 --> 00:23:34,400
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">只要认可就好</font>

494
00:23:34,590 --> 00:23:37,440
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}だからそうさ君がやっと</font>

495
00:23:34,590 --> 00:23:37,440
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">因此请让我对你说</font>

496
00:23:37,570 --> 00:23:39,720
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}絶望の先で</font>

497
00:23:37,570 --> 00:23:39,720
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">在我绝望的时候</font>

498
00:23:39,910 --> 00:23:48,910
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}くれた日々に偽りなんてないと言ってあげよう</font>

499
00:23:39,910 --> 00:23:48,910
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">你曾给我带来的那些日子没有虚假</font>

500
00:23:50,600 --> 00:23:54,890
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}忘れないで</font>

501
00:23:50,600 --> 00:23:54,890
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">不要将我忘记</font>

502
00:23:59,950 --> 00:24:00,910
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（四个月后）</font>

503
00:24:04,600 --> 00:24:07,470
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那么…那之后又怎么样了？</font>

504
00:24:07,780 --> 00:24:10,640
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">应该说是后日谈吧  这次的结局</font>

505
00:24:10,940 --> 00:24:12,790
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">并没有发生什么</font>

506
00:24:13,300 --> 00:24:18,440
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">在那之后八九寺顺利成佛  我和斧乃木妹妹又回到了这镇上</font>

507
00:24:18,670 --> 00:24:21,420
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后按照约定帮卧烟小姐做了工作</font>

508
00:24:21,900 --> 00:24:24,800
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">要说事件  那边那个才算是大事件呢</font>

509
00:24:25,070 --> 00:24:28,430
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">啊  真是不容易啊  我了解了</font>

510
00:24:28,430 --> 00:24:28,640
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（结果我什么都没做）</font>

511
00:24:28,640 --> 00:24:28,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（一直被牵着鼻子走）</font>

512
00:24:28,930 --> 00:24:29,310
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（被八九寺）</font>

513
00:24:29,310 --> 00:24:29,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（——被命运）</font>

514
00:24:29,940 --> 00:24:34,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">现在我还是会想  那时是不是还有别的什么办法</font>

515
00:24:34,560 --> 00:24:36,960
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">哎呀  可以说是勉强通过了吧</font>

516
00:24:37,240 --> 00:24:42,880
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">比起被黑暗吞掉  自己选择去成佛是相当明智的</font>

517
00:24:43,960 --> 00:24:48,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">真是听了个好故事  谢谢你了  阿良良木学长</font>

518
00:24:48,460 --> 00:24:51,460
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不  说了这些我也感觉痛快许多</font>

519
00:24:51,680 --> 00:24:54,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不不  谢还是要谢的</font>

520
00:24:54,620 --> 00:24:59,430
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那么我还有许多工作  今天就先回去了</font>

521
00:24:59,910 --> 00:25:02,800
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我说  小扇  你所说的工作是什么？</font>

522
00:25:03,040 --> 00:25:04,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">很普通的工作啦</font>

523
00:25:04,860 --> 00:25:10,320
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">打个比方的话  就像占据宇宙大部分的黑暗一样平常的工作</font>

524
00:25:10,800 --> 00:25:14,200
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">把错的东西纠正  把该结束的东西画上休止符</font>

525
00:25:14,540 --> 00:25:17,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">硬要说的话  就像给撒谎的人加以惩罚一样</font>

526
00:25:19,310 --> 00:25:21,620
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你早晚会明白的  请放心</font>

527
00:25:22,230 --> 00:25:27,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没准之后还有要请阿良良木学长帮忙的地方</font>

528
00:25:28,180 --> 00:25:28,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">回见</font>

529
00:25:32,470 --> 00:25:36,470
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">总觉得大家都抛下我走掉了</font>

530
00:25:37,220 --> 00:25:39,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">有种被抛弃的感觉</font>

531
00:25:39,140 --> 00:25:42,230
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">汝啊  吾想汝也应该知道吧</font>

532
00:25:42,380 --> 00:25:45,010
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那个女人  多半是个人物</font>

533
00:25:45,520 --> 00:25:48,470
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">啊  是啊  也许是</font>

534
00:25:48,660 --> 00:25:50,640
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">什么嘛  汝知道啊</font>

535
00:25:50,840 --> 00:25:53,710
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不…全都是些我不知道的事情</font>

536
00:25:54,030 --> 00:25:55,850
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我真的很想知道  什么都好</font>

537
00:25:56,980 --> 00:25:57,270
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（总是去想那些想了也没有用的事情）</font>

538
00:25:57,270 --> 00:25:57,560
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（也感觉了结了几个  不该了结的事）</font>

539
00:25:57,560 --> 00:25:57,940
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（就连为那些事而伤心的感觉）</font>

540
