554
00:26:40,240 --> 00:26:41,710
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">怎么可能</font>

555
00:26:42,820 --> 00:26:43,150
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（提着书包）</font>

556
00:26:43,150 --> 00:26:43,570
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（我准备回家）</font>

557
00:26:45,070 --> 00:26:45,400
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（踏上了回家的路）</font>

558
00:26:46,650 --> 00:26:47,030
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（踏上已不会再遇到任何人的——回家路）</font>

559
00:26:47,350 --> 00:26:50,150
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说起来  四个月前的那一天</font>

560
00:26:50,630 --> 00:26:53,910
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我直到分开也没和八九寺说出那句话</font>

561
00:26:54,660 --> 00:26:58,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">到现在才发觉这件事  我也真是够粗心的了</font>

562
00:27:01,960 --> 00:27:04,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">「再见了  八九寺真宵」</font>

563
00:27:05,080 --> 00:27:07,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">「和你相遇  我感到很幸福」</font>

564
00:27:11,010 --> 00:27:11,720
<font face="@FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an7}火怜DaZe！</font>

565
00:27:11,040 --> 00:27:11,710
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">火怜Da☆Ze！</font>

566
00:27:11,720 --> 00:27:12,430
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">月火Da☆Yo！</font>

