569
00:27:12,640 --> 00:27:14,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">两个人合在一起就是Fire Sisters！</font>

570
00:27:14,510 --> 00:27:26,860
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}其实是来接真宵妹妹
回家的么？</font>

571
00:27:14,750 --> 00:27:17,550
