572
00:27:17,550 --> 00:27:18,870
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">还能出BD呢</font>

573
00:27:18,870 --> 00:27:22,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">大家都把我们的预告篇简称为「姐预」</font>

574
00:27:22,280 --> 00:27:23,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我怎么没听说</font>

575
00:27:23,140 --> 00:27:24,060
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">预告篇Quiz！</font>

576
00:27:24,060 --> 00:27:24,630
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">Quiz！</font>

577
00:27:24,630 --> 00:27:26,110
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">「翅意喂够」  知道不知道？</font>

578
00:27:26,110 --> 00:27:28,440
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">知道知道  都快知道烂…嗯？</font>

579
00:27:26,860 --> 00:27:39,200
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}哎？要告别了？</font>

580
00:27:28,560 --> 00:27:30,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">怎么了  月火</font>

581
00:27:30,150 --> 00:27:32,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说得好像源氏物语第十四帖卷名一样</font>

582
00:27:32,670 --> 00:27:34,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">「翅意喂够」是啥？</font>

583
00:27:34,110 --> 00:27:36,600
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">翅翼？还是「鸡翅意面喂你管够」的意思？</font>

584
00:27:36,710 --> 00:27:38,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">什么嘛  你不知道啊</font>

585
00:27:38,340 --> 00:27:42,070
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就是把词汇的词序进行易位  构成其他词汇的文字游戏</font>

586
00:27:39,200 --> 00:27:51,470
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}啊！成佛了！</font>

587
00:27:42,070 --> 00:27:43,300
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那不是「易位构词」吗？</font>

588
00:27:43,300 --> 00:27:47,430
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">把「易位构词」易位成「翅意喂够」  举了个栗子</font>

589
00:27:47,430 --> 00:27:48,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这哪算什么例子</font>

590
00:27:48,750 --> 00:27:51,420
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那我就再举一个  「凉啊凉木莲火」</font>

591
00:27:51,470 --> 00:28:03,730
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}这么重要的时候哥哥居然不在</font>

592
00:27:51,670 --> 00:27:57,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">把这个词易位就是「阿良良木火怜」是也！</font>

593
00:27:57,280 --> 00:28:01,390
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">啊好厉害  把「凉啊凉木莲火」易位就成了「阿良良木火怜」</font>

594
00:28:02,080 --> 00:28:03,550
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">「凉啊凉木莲火」又是啥玩意？</font>

595
00:28:03,920 --> 00:28:05,880
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">下集  恋物语  第一话</font>

596
00:28:05,980 --> 00:28:07,160
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">黑仪与结局  其一</font>

597
00:28:07,320 --> 00:28:10,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">把「量啊量火月木」易位就成了「阿良良木月火」</font>

598
00:28:07,320 --> 00:28:15,320
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}在听人讲整整400年的故事</font>

599
00:28:10,220 --> 00:28:12,590
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就成我了？「良月良火木啊」？</font>

